oards-windows-copilot-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20addition%20will%20allow%20users%20to%20access%20Microsoft's%20AI%20companion%2C%20Copilot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-button-pc-keyboards-windows-copilot-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pannun%20'Murder%20Plot'%3A%20SC%20Junks%20Plea%20Against%20Nikhil%20Gupta's%20Arrest%2C%20Cites%20Lack%20of%20Jurisdiction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20rejected%20the%20plea%20of%20the%20family%20members%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20detention%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20and%20is%20accused%20in%20the%20alleged%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20US-based%20Khalistani%20activist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Csensitive%E2%80%9D%20matter%20and%20said%20it%20is%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment%20to%20take%20action%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20is%20a%20sensitive%20matter%20for%20the%20government%20also.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20ramifications.%20We%20will%20not%20in%20this%20court%20make%20any%20statement.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20government%20to%20do%20what%20they%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-nikhil-gupta-pannun-murder-plot-case-9094647%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20public%20international%20law%20and%20comity%20of%20courts%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20intervene.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20accused%20Gupta%20of%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20an%20Indian%20intelligence%20official.%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20June%20last%20year%20and%20Czech%20courts%20are%20considering%20his%20extradition%2C%20as%20requested%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Dipankar%20Datta%20also%20concurred%20with%20the%20view%20of%20his%20fellow%20judge.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20examined%20the%20prayers%20made%20in%20the%20present%20writ%20petition.%20Keeping%20in%20view%20the%20principles%20of%20public%20international%20law%20and%20sovereignty%20and%20comity%20of%20courts%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20any%20of%20the%20prayers%20can%20be%20granted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20kin%20told%20the%20court%20the%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20his%20arrest%20had%20been%20marked%20by%20%E2%80%9Cirregularities%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20outset%2C%20the%20petitioner%20contends%20that%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20his%20arrest%20were%20marked%20by%20irregularities%2C%20with%20no%20formal%20arrest%20warrant%20presented%2C%20and%20the%20apprehension%20executed%20by%20self-claimed%20US%20agents%20rather%20than%20local%20Czech%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-rejects-petition-by-family-members-of-nikhil-gupta-indicted-by-us-in-pannun-murder-plot-101704346298067.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20petitioner%20was%20not%20shown%20any%20arrest%20warrant%20during%20the%20initial%20detention.%20Instead%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20individuals%20purporting%20to%20represent%20US%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20submission%20by%20Gupta%E2%80%