%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20California%20restaurant%20%26quot%3Bmisappropriated%26quot%3B%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20tips%20to%20fund%20business%20expenses%2C%20the%20DOL%20claims.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20restaurant%20deposited%20tips%20into%20its%20business%20account%20and%20gave%20a%20portion%20to%20staff%20each%20week%2C%20the%20DOL%20claims.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20DOL%20accused%20it%20of%20violating%20the%20Fair%20Labor%20Standards%20Act.%20It's%20seeking%20%24500%2C000%20for%20staff.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20French%20restaurant%20in%20Pasadena%2C%20California%20took%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20tips%20from%20servers%2C%20runners%2C%20and%20bartenders%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisappropriated%26quot%3B%20them%20to%20fund%20business%20expenses%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor%20has%20claimed%20in%20a%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOL%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%202%20Poto%2C%20the%20operators%20of%20Entre%20Nous%20French%20Bistro%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20violated%20the%20Fair%20Labor%20Standards%20Act.%20It's%20seeking%20%24500%2C000%20for%20affected%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Central%20District%20of%20California%20on%20December%2028%2C%20says%20that%20owners%20Jean-Christophe%20Febbrari%20and%20Mathias%20Wakrat%20kept%20a%20portion%20of%20employees'%20tips%20to%20use%20for%20business%20expenses.%C2%A0The%20upmarket%20restaurant%2C%20which%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entrenousfrenchbistro.com%2Fmenu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2450%20minimum%20spend%20per%20diner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deposited%20both%20cash%20and%20card%20tips%20into%20its%20business%20account%20and%20distributed%20only%20a%20portion%20to%20staff%20via%20a%20weekly%20wire%20transfer%2C%20the%20DOL%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20week%20from%20December%2021%2C%202021%2C%20customers%20left%20about%20%2412%2C500%20in%20credit%20card%20tips%2C%20but%20the%20restaurant%20gave%20less%20than%20%247%2C600%20of%20this%20to%20staff%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20keep%20staff%20tips%20%26quot%3Bunder%20any%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Fwhd%2Fflsa%2Ftips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFLSA%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20stipulates.%20If%20a%20restaurant%20operates%20an%20illegal%20tip%20pool%2C%20for%20example%20by%20sharing%20tips%20with%20owners%20and%20managers%2C%20it%20invalidates%20its%20claims%20to%20a%20tip%20credit%2C%20which%20can%20sometimes%20push%20workers'%20wages%20under%20the%20minimum%20wage%2C%20as%20the%20DOL%20has%20said%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-restaurant-made-servers-share-tips-with-owners-managers-dol-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20investigations%20into%20tip%20violations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOL%20says%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20amid%20its%20investigation%2C%20Entre%20Nous%20introduced%20a%20no-tip%20policy%20in%20May%202023%2C%20instead%20collecting%20a%2020%25%20service%20charge.%20But%20some%20customers%20still%20leave%20cash%20tips%2C%20which%20the%20restaurant%20keeps%2C%20the%20DOL%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntre%20Nous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entrenousfrenchbistro.com%2Fmenu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20menu%20that%20the%20fee%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20a%20gratuity%20or%20tip.%26quot%3B%20It%20variously%20lists%20the%20fee%20as%2020%25%20and%2018%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fee%20is%20revenue%20that%20is%20not%20segmented%20or%20designated%20in%20any%20way%3B%20it%20is%20taxed%20per%20state%20law%20and%20is%20used%20to%20fund%20all%20of%20our%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOL%20also%20claims%20that%20its%20investigation%20into%20Entre%20Nous%20found%20that%20the%20restaurant%20misclassified%20several%20employees%20as%20independent%20contractors%20and%20didn't%20keep%20accurate%20pay%20records%2C%20including%20failing%20to%20record%20all%20tips%20staff%20received%20and%20record%20all%20hours%20they%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20practices%20violate%20the%20FLSA%2C%20the%20DOL%20claims.%20Though%20the%20lawsuit%20doesn't%20name%20a%20dollar%20amount%2C%20the%20DOL%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Freleases%2Fwhd%2Fwhd20240103-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20seeking%20%24250%2C000%20in%20back%20wages%20and%20an%20equal%20amount%20in%20liquidated%20damages%20for%2018%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntre%20Nous%20has%20an%204.6-star%20rating%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FEntre%2BNous%2BFrench%2BBistro%2F%4034.1447734%2C-118.1556051%2C17z%2Fdata%3D!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x80c2c3970d93b5b1%3A0xa385570aaf105039!8m2!3d34.144769!4d-118.1530302!16s%252Fg%252F11gxpx6v1q%3Fentry%3Dttu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%204.5-star%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yelp.com%2Fbiz%2Fentre-nous-french-bistro-pasadena-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYelp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Entrees%20at%20the%20restaurant%20start%20at%20%2429.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20contacted%20Entre%20Nous%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20did%20not%20immediately%20receive%20a%20response%2C%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-restaurant-took-servers-tips-staff-dol-pasadena-flsa-workers-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704368660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-restaurant-took-servers-tips-staff-dol-pasadena-flsa-workers-2024-1%22%2C