ardas%E2%80%A6Modi%20have%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%E2%80%99d%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20lawyers%20had%20told%20the%20top%20court%20that%20this%20was%20a%20slip%20of%20the%20tongue%20and%20he%20had%20apologised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remark%20led%20to%20multiple%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20and%20his%20subsequent%20arrest%20by%20Assam%20police%20in%20the%20same%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20arrest%20on%20February%2023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsupreme-court-grants-interim-bail-to-detained-congress-leader-pawan-khera%2Farticle66544500.ece%5C%22%3Egranted%3C%2Fa%3E%20temporary%20relief%20to%20Khera%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20It%20directed%20his%20release%20on%20interim%20bail%20till%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20interim%20relief%20period%20was%20extended%20first%20until%20March%203%2C%20and%20later%20again%20until%20March%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-pawan-khera-congress-narendra-gautam-das-modi-245836%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Khera%20is%20facing%20charges%20under%20Sections%20153A%20(promoting%20communal%20enmity)%2C%20153B%20(imputations%20prejudicial%20to%20national%20integration)%2C%20500%20(defamation)%2C%20504%20(insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%20and%20other%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20had%20said%20that%20Khera%20had%20made%20the%20comment%20inadvertently%20and%20his%20prompt%20apology%20was%20issued%20in%20a%20separate%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20He%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20charges%20levelled%20against%20Khera%2C%20which%20include%20that%20of%20defamation%2C%20attempting%20to%20degrade%20and%20destablise%20the%20nation%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20and%20hatred%20between%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20disturbing%20public%20peace%20were%20a%20%E2%80%98complete%20stretch%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhera%20had%20also%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20seeking%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20summons%20order%20and%20chargesheet%20filed%20against%20him.%20He%20also%20issued%20an%20unconditional%20apology%20for%20the%20purported%20incident%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20previously%20refused%20to%20quash%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704366754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-refuses-to-quash-criminal-case-against-congresss-pawan-khera-over-narendra-modi-name-remark%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20February%20last%20year%2C%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20affair%2C%20Khera%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-refuses-to-quash-criminal-case-against-congresss-pawan-khera-over-narendra-modi-name-remark%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22REC%2C%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20join%20hands%20to%20finance%20power%2C%20infra%2C%20logistics%20projects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704366729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F09%2Ffull%2F1694235263-8444.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frec-bank-of-baroda-join-hands-to-finance-power-infra-logistics-projects-124010400685_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22State-owned%20REC%20Ltd%20has%20inked%20an%20initial%20pact%20with%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20to%20jointly%20