20leader%20with%20a%20warmth%20towards%20people%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20had%20privately%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20begin%20from%20Imphal%20at%2012.30%20pm.%20It%20will%20pass%20through%20Manipur%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Assam%2C%20Arunanchal%20Pradesh%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20went%20Bengal%20before%20reaching%20central%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20last%20time%20though%2C%20the%20Yatra%20will%20not%20be%20entirely%20on%20foot.%20For%20parts%20of%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20party%20will%20use%20buses%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20told%20reporters%20this%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20is%20as%20much%20due%20to%20time%20constraint%20imposed%20by%20the%20general%20election%20as%20the%20health%20concerns%20of%20the%20party's%20elderly%20leaders.%20More%20than%20one%20leader%20had%20made%20headlines%20last%20year%20due%20to%20the%20exertion%20they%20faced%2C%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20superbly%20fit%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20inviting%20leaders%20of%20all%20the%20parties%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20their%20supporters%2C%20the%20general%20public%20and%20NGOs%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20yatra%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20not%20pulled%20punches%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20concerned%20%E2%80%93%20will%20be%20invited%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said%20all%20parties%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20been%20invited.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20AAP%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20are%20part%20of%20INDIA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Chief%20Ministers%20belonging%20to%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20will%20be%20present%20at%20Imphal%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20yatra%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704366540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fqs8s517_rahul-gandhi-bharat-