get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArvia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20ship%20was%20launched%20in%202022%20by%20the%20British%20cruise%20line%20P%26amp%3BO%20and%20has%2019%20decks%2C%2030%20bars%20and%20restaurants%2C%20and%20the%20capacity%20to%20host%205%2C200%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArvia%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farvia-uk-largest-cruise-caribbean-review-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E%20built%20for%20the%20UK%20market%2C%20a%20P%26amp%3BO%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20It's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20cruise%20ships%20in%20the%20world%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fholiday-types%2Fcruises%2Fworlds-biggest-cruise-ships%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Times%20of%20London%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20marked%20my%20partner's%20first%20time%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship.%20I%20had%20cruised%20once%20before%2C%20on%20a%20five-night%20voyage%20around%20northern%20Europe%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farvia-uk-largest-cruise-caribbean-review-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECunard's%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20capacity%20to%20host%20just%20over%202%2C000%20guests%2C%20the%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fyoungest-guest-on-luxury-cruise-friends-in-their-70s-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efar%20smaller%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20Arvia.%20I%20soon%20realized%20that%20my%20previous%20cruise%20experience%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20prepare%20me%20for%20this%20trip%2C%20and%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20there%20were%20strict%20rules%20surrounding%20deck%20chairs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deck%20chairs%20on%20Arvia%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6595777b1c5c7b8c9a0d8eb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeck%20chairs%20on%20Arvia.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20previous%20cruise%20took%20place%20in%20northern%20Europe%20during%20the%20fall%2C%20which%20meant%20it%20was%20far%20too%20cold%20to%20sunbathe%20or%20relax%20in%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20be%20sailing%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20where%20the%20weather%20is%20typically%20warm%20and%20sunny%20in%20December.%20On%20our%20first%20sea%20day%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-you-should-never-do-on-cruises-according-to-crew-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeager%20to%20get%20a%20deck%20chair%20by%20the%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20we%20arrived%20shortly%20after%20breakfast%2C%20all%20the%20seats%20were%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20next%20sea%20day%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later%2C%20my%20partner%20woke%20up%20at%206%20a.m.%20to%20reserve%20two%20deck%20chairs%20with%20towels.%20We%20figured%20this%20would%20be%20OK%2C%20as%20we%20noticed%20several%20chairs%20with%20towels%20over%20them%20on%20our%20first%20sea%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20we%20went%20back%20after%20having%20breakfast%2C%20our%20towels%20had%20been%20removed%20by%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20guests%20aren't%20supposed%20to%20leave%20deck%20chairs%20unaccompanied%20for%20longer%20than%2030%20minutes%2C%20or%20an%20employee%20could%20remove%20their%20towel.%20And%20we%20weren't%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20didn't%20know%20the%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20we%20witnessed%20several%20other%20guests%20arguing%20over%20deck%20chair%20etiquette%20throughout%20the%20cruise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20didn't%20budget%20enough%20spending%20money%20for%20the%20ship%20or%20the%20ports.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mikhaila%20tortola%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6595795dec62ab5daf804372%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20pictured%20at%20the%20cruise%20port%20in%20Tortola.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20ported%20in%20Tortola%2C%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%2C%20St.%20Maarten%2C%20Antigua%2C%20St.%20Kitts%2C%20Martinique%2C%20St.%20Lucia%2C%20and%20Barbados.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20had%20an%20amazing%20time%20exploring%20each%20port.%20Every%20place%20had%20something%20unique%20to%20offer%2C%20from%20underground%20caves%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20to%20bustling%20beachside%20restaurants%20and%20bars%20in%20St.%20Maarten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20spending%20more%20money%20than%20we%20had%20initially%20intended%2C%20as%20we%20hadn't%20planned%20for%20some%20of%20the%20hidden%20expenses.%20Almost%20every%20beach%20we%20visited%20charged%20guests%20up%20to%20%2430%20to%20use%20deck%20chairs%20and%20umbrellas%2C%20and%20one%20we%20visited%20in%20St.%20Lucia%20charged%20guests%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20of%20taxis%20also%20varied%20significantly%20in%20each%20port.%20In%20Martinique%2C%20one%20taxi%20driver%20tried%20to%20charge%20me%20and%20my%20partner%20%2440%20each%20for%20a%2040-minute%2C%20one-way%20journey%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20which%20we%20declined%20before%20finding%20a%20slightly%20cheaper%20taxi.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20St.%20Lucia%2C%20a%2040-minute%20taxi%20from%20the%20cruise%20port%20to%20Pigeon%20Island%20cost%20%2430%20per%20person%20for%20a%20roundtrip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20ship%2C%20most%20of%20the%20activities%20and%20entertainment%20were%20free.%20However%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhat-to-pay-extra-for-on-cruise-ship-worth-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20money%20on%20extra%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20sea%20days.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20took%20part%20in%20an%20obstacle%20course%20on%20board%2C%20which%20cost%20%C2%A37.50%2C%20or%20around%20%249.50%2C%20per%20person%2C%20and%20a%20submarine-themed%20escape%20room%2C%20which%20cost%20%C2%A320%2C%20or%20around%20%2425%2C%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stuck%20to%20the%20free%20restaurants%20for%20most%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20but%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20voyage%2C%20we%20booked%20tickets%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pocruises.com%2Fonboard-activities%2Fdining%2Fthe-limelight-club%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Limelight%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%C2%A325%2C%20or%20around%20%2431%2C%20per%20person.%20The%20tickets%20included%20a%20three-course%20meal%20and%20a%20performance%20from%20theatre%20actor%20Joel%20Harper-Jackson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20take%20cash%20out%20at%20reception%20for%20the%20ports%20and%20the%20additional%20expenses%20on%20board%20were%20charged%20to%20our%20cruise%20card.%20Ultimately%2C%20we%20didn't%20regret%20spending%20a%20bit%20more%20as%20we%20had%20a%20great%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20I%20ever%20go%20on%20a%20cruise%20again%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20to%20factor%20additional%20costs%20into%20my%20budget%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20pre-book%20dinner%20for%20celebration%20nights.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mikhaila%20cruise%20ship%20celebration%20night%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659578f0ab6f2ebb11f86ff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20pictured%20during%20Celebration%20Night.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20cruise%20hosted%20two%20celebration%20nights%2C%20also%20known%20as%20formal%20nights%2C%20where%20guests%20were%20asked%20to%20dress%20in%20evening%20attire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dress%20code%20wasn't%20mandatory%20throughout%20the%20ship%2C%20but%20it%20was%20expected%20for%20those%20attending%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pocruises.com%2Fonboard-activities%2Fdining%2Fcelebration-night%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebration%20dinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20five-course%20menu%20created%20by%20celebrity%20chef%20Marco%20Pierre%20White%20%E2%80%94%20served%20at%20two%20of%20the%20ship's%20main%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20tried%20to%20book%20a%20table%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20first%20celebration%20night%2C%20we%20were%20told%20both%20restaurants%20serving%20the%20specialty%20menu%20were%20fully%20booked.%20For%20the%20second%20celebration%20night%2C%20we%20attempted%20to%20book%20a%20table%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20in%20advance%20and%20found%20they%20had%20once%20again%20been%20fully%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20we%20were%20allocated%20a%20table%20on%20both%20nights%20after%20waiting%20for%20the%20guests%20who%20had%20pre-booked%20to%20finish%20their%20meals.%20We%20spent%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20waiting%20in%20a%20virtual%20queue%2C%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20it%20as%20the%20food%20was%20exceptional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20completely%20different%20from%20my%20experience%20on%20the%20Queen%20Elizabeth%2C%20where%20every%20guest%20was%20allocated%20a%20table%20on%20the%20day.%20Looking%20back%2C%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20expected%20the%20same%20treatment%20since%20Arvia%20is%20a%20much%20larger%20cruise%20during%20a%20peak%20travel%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20P%26amp%3BO%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20specialty%20dining%20on%20Arvia%20is%20available%20to%20book%20online%20two%20weeks%20before%20departure%20and%20that%20guests%20are%20welcome%20to%20check%20the%20restaurants%20for%20availability%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20to%20plan%20ahead%20and%20book%20a%20table%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-made-uk-largest-cruise-ship-arvia-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704365719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659579f9ab6f2ebb11f87085%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-made-uk-largest-cruise-ship-arvia-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider's%20reporter%20spent%20two%20weeks%20on%20P%26amp%3BO's%20Arvia%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20cruise%20ships%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfriel%40insider.com%20(Mikhaila%20Friel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-made-uk-largest-cruise-ship-arvia-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boney%20spent%202%20hours%20hunting%20a%20Pink%20Taxi%20for%20Khushi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704365408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106545269%2Cimgsize-84088.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-boney-kapoor-spent-two-hours-hunting-a-pink-taxi-for-daughter-khushi-kapoor-in-london%2Farticleshow%2F106545260.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106545260.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJanhvi%20and%20Khushi%20Kapoor%20shared%20childhood%20secrets%20and%20insights%20into%20their%20bond%20on%20Koffee%20with%20Kar