%2C%20the%20body%20was%20taken%20to%20Singh's%20BMW%2C%20driven%20somewhere%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Punjab%20and%20dumped.%20The%20police%20are%20yet%20to%20locate%20the%20body%20and%20have%20launched%20a%20massive%20hunt%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPahuja%2C%2027%2C%20was%20in%20jail%20for%20seven%20years%20for%20her%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20fake%20encounter%20of%20her%20then%20boyfriend%20and%20Gurugram%20gangster%20Sandeep%20Gadoli%20in%202016.%20She%20had%20been%20granted%20bail%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20Hotel%20City%20Point's%20reception%2C%20which%20has%20a%20timestamp%20of%204.18%20am%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20shows%20Singh%2C%20Pahuja%20and%20another%20man%20walking%20in.%20Singh%20and%20the%20other%20person%20can%20be%20seen%20speaking%20to%20the%20receptionist%20while%20Pahuja%20stands%20behind%20them.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%2C%20Singh%20and%20Pahuja%20walk%20further%20into%20the%20hotel%20while%20the%20other%20person%20says%20something%20to%20the%20receptionist%2C%20before%20heading%20in%20their%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20video%2C%20said%20to%20be%20from%20around%2010.45%20pm%2C%20shows%20two%20men%20dragging%20Pahuja's%20body%2C%20wrapped%20in%20a%20blanket%2C%20down%20a%20corridor%20of%20the%20hotel.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20is%20later%20seen%20walking%20back.%20Police%20said%20the%20body%20was%20carried%20to%20a%20blue%20BMW%20owned%20by%20Singh%20and%20disposed%20of.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlackmail%20Angle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Pahuja%20allegedly%20had%20some%20obscene%20videos%20of%20Singh%20on%20her%20phone%20which%20he%20asked%20her%20to%20delete%2C%20but%20she%20refused.%20The%20former%20model%20was%20allegedly%20blackmailing%20the%20hotel%20owner%20with%20the%20photos%20and%20this%20led%20to%20Singh%20and%20at%20least%20two%20of%20his%20aides%20shooting%20her.%20Pahuja's%20family%20has%20vehemently%20denied%20this%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20and%20two%20of%20his%20alleged%20accomplices%2C%20Omprakash%20and%20Hemraj%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Police%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20two%20or%20three%20other%20aides%2C%20who%20were%20allegedly%20paid%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20by%20Singh%20to%20dispose%20of%20Pahuja's%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2016%20Encounter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPahuja%20was%20the%20alleged%20girlfriend%20of%20Gurugram's%20most-wanted%20gangster%20Sandeep%20Gadoli%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20police%20in%20an%20encounter%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20hotel%20in%202016.%20The%20former%20model%20was%20in%20the%20hotel%20room%20with%20Gadoli%20when%20he%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20police%20officials%20were%20later%20arrested%20when%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20the%20encounter%20was%20fake.%20Pahuja%20and%20her%20mother%20were%20also%20taken%20into%20custody%20for%20allegedly%20revealing%20the%20gangster's%20whereabouts%20and%20facilitating%20the%20%26quot%3Bfake%20encounter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPahuja%20was%20in%20prison%20since%202016%20and%20had%20been%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704364740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9iilma68_divya-pahuja_625x300_04_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdivya-pahuja-murder-gurugram-murder-sandeep-gadoli-cctv-footage-reveals-last-sighting-of-former-model-divya-pahujas-body-4798645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CCTV%20footage%20recovered%20from%20the%20Gurugram%20hotel%20where%20former%20model%20Divya%20Pahuja%20was%20shot%20dead%20has%20helped%20the%20police%20piece%20together%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20murder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdivya-pahuja-murder-gurugram-murder-