ed%20and%20let%20out%20a%20stream%20of%20expletives%20while%20I%20held%20the%20receiver%20away%20from%20my%20ear!%20Many%20months%20later%2C%20he%20called%20again.%20This%20time%20he%20started%20his%20pitch%20by%20saying%20-%20%E2%80%9Cit's%20the%20lead%20role%20so%20don't%20reject%20it%E2%80%9D.%20And%20that's%20how%20I%20joined%20the%20cast%20of%20%3Cem%3EQurbani%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20one%20of%20her%20biggest%20hits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20often%20discuss%20set%20etiquette%20in%20my%20captions%2C%20so%20I'd%20be%20amiss%20to%20neglect%20Feroz's%20influence%20on%20me%20in%20this%20regard.%20I%20was%20quite%20a%20diligent%20worker%2C%20but%20on%20one%20occasion%20my%20youth%20got%20the%20better%20of%20me.%20Though%20we%20had%20an%20early%20call%20time%20the%20next%20day%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20go%20out%20to%20a%20party.%20It%20was%20a%20fantastic%20night%20of%20dance%20and%20drink%2C%20and%20unsurprisingly%20I%20landed%20up%20one%20hour%20late%20to%20set.%20Feroz%20was%20glowering%20behind%20his%20monitor%2C%20and%20before%20I%20could%20offer%20him%20my%20meagre%20excuse%2C%20he%20cut%20me%20down%20to%20size.%20%E2%80%9CBegum%2C%20you're%20late%20and%20you're%20going%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20delay.%E2%80%9D%20No%20argument%2C%20no%20scolding%2C%20but%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20he%20docked%20my%20pay%20to%20pay%20the%20crew%20for%20that%20one%20hour%20delay!%E2%80%9D%20Summing%20up%20her%20thoughts%20about%20Feroz%20Khan%2C%20the%20actress%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFeroz%20was%20suave%2C%20charming%20and%20polished.%20He%20was%20a%20talented%20actor-director%2C%20and%20Qurbani%20remains%20one%20of%20my%20favourite%20projects%20to%20date.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20enjoyed%20this%20anecdote%20and%20I%20hope%202024%20is%20off%20to%20a%20roaring%20start%20for%20you!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20post%2C%20Maria%20Goretti%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BHeart%20emojis%5D%20and%20what%20a%20film%20that%20is%20to%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActress%20Sumalatha%20Ambareesh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20precious%20anecdotes%20about%20the%20behind-the-scenes%20workings%20of%20movies%20we%20adored.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector-writer%20Tanuja%20Chandra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20stories%20are%20fascinating%20to%20read.%20And%20always%20fun.%20Awaiting%20that%20biography.%20You%20might%20want%20to%20name%20it%20Begum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiandra%20Soares%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20beautiful%20share%2C%C2%A0%20and%20you%20both%20and%20this%20film.%20Uff.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActress%20Delnaaz%20Irani%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThank%20you%20for%20sharing%20loved%20the%20movie%20and%20of%20course%20the%20music%20was%20a%20rage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1qt6VJi2Sz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1qt6VJi2Sz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1qt6VJi2Sz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv