2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.balldrop.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3E%20led%20me%20to%20Balldrop.com%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20website%20that%20features%20a%20variety%20of%20ticketed%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20events%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20I%20soon%20learned%20most%20of%20the%20parties%20only%20accommodated%20guests%2021%20and%20older.%20Since%20the%20exchange%20student%20who%20we%20were%20hosting%20was%20only%2018%20years%20old%20we%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20party%20catering%20to%20all%20ages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20soon%20became%20clear%20the%20best%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-spending-hundreds-dollars-new-year-ball-drop-chain-restaurants-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echoice%20for%20us%20was%20Applebee's.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20All%20of%20this%2C%20of%20course%2C%20came%20at%20a%20price.%20Our%20three%20tickets%2C%20which%20were%20the%20least%20expensive%20option%2C%20cost%20%24699%20a%20piece.%20After%20taxes%20and%20service%20charges%20the%20total%20came%20to%20just%20over%20%242%2C500.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20I%20spent%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20at%20Applebee's%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20the%20other%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20festivities%2C%20despite%20their%20high%20ticket%20prices%2C%20only%20offered%20a%20televised%20streaming%20of%20the%20ball%20drop%20or%20a%20view%20from%20a%20window%20or%20terrace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20figured%20if%20we%20were%20making%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-new-york-city%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etrip%20to%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20specifically%20for%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20should%20do%20whatever%20we%20could%20to%20get%20as%20close%20to%20the%20action%20as%20possible.%20Applebee's%20was%20not%20only%20family-friendly%20and%20open%20to%20all%20ages%20but%2C%20barring%20any%20unforeseen%20security%20issues%2C%20all%20ticket%20holders%20were%20escorted%20to%20the%20street%20and%20granted%20access%20to%20a%20dedicated%20area%20behind%20barricades%20for%20a%20live%20view%20of%20the%20ball%20drop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20bought%20the%20cheapest%20seats%2C%20but%20they%20were%20the%20best%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20that%20price%2C%20we%20each%20had%20a%20window-facing%20high-top%20counter%20seat%20in%20the%20bar%20area%20of%20the%20Applebee's%20on%2050th%20Street%20between%20Broadway%20and%20Seventh%20Avenue%2C%20a%20few%20blocks%20away%20from%20the%20ball%20drop%20on%20West%2043rd%20Street.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20they%20were%20the%20cheapest%20seats%20in%20the%20house%2C%20I%20think%20they%20were%20the%20best%20because%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fshould-i-visit-times-square-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eviews%20of%20Times%20Square%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20provided%20us%20with%20plenty%20of%20great%20people-watching.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHigher-priced%20tickets%20came%20with%20seats%20at%20an%20actual%20table%20but%20the%20best%20bang%20for%20our%20buck%20were%20the%20bar%20stools.%20We%20got%20guaranteed%20seating%20and%20all-inclusive%20access%20to%20everything%20that%20everyone%20else%20got%20for%20less%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20food%20was%20more%20high-end%20than%20I%20expected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENormally%2C%20I'm%20not%20an%20Applebee's%20guy%2C%20but%20I'll%20go%20there%20on%20occasion.%20I%20mostly%20go%20if%20I'm%20traveling%20on%20business%20and%20need%20to%20grab%20a%20quick%20bite%2C%20but%20on%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20they%20take%20everything%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20The%20food%20isn't%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fapplebees-two-people-appetizers-entree-review-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyour%20typical%20Applebee's%20fare%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It's%20much%20more%20high-end%20than%20I%20ever%20expected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20passed%20hors%20d'oeuvres%20including%20items%20like%20avocado%20and%20shrimp%20ceviche%20and%20chicken%20wontons%2C%20a%20full%20buffet%20including%20steak%20and%20salmon%2C%20and%20an%20assortment%20of%20desserts.%20There's%20also%20a%20premium%20top-shelf%20open%20bar%20for%20guests%2021%20and%20older%20and%20different%20types%20of%20specialty%20cocktails%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Champagne%20toast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20part%20is%20that%20twenty%20minutes%20before%20midnight%20all%20400%20Applebee's%20guests%20are%20personally%20escorted%20outside%20to%20a%20designated%20area%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-years-eve-ball-drop-tradition-sailors-times-square-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewatch%20the%20ball%20drop%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There's%20no%20waiting%20in%20the%20cold%20for%20hours%20or%20fighting%20to%20get%20a%20good%20spot.%20We%20literally%20just%20have%20to%20walk%20outside%20and%20head%20to%20the%20corner%20for%20a%20clear%2C%20unobstructed%20view%20of%20the%20ball.%20You%20can't%20beat%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20used%20hotel%20points%20and%20airline%20miles%20to%20cover%20our%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20trip%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20ball%20drop%2C%20the%20party%20is%20over%20and%20since%20our%20hotel%2C%20the%20Marriott%20Marquis%2C%20was%20only%20a%20few%20blocks%20away%2C%20we%20were%20back%20in%20our%20hotel%20room%20within%20fifteen%20minutes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C