Findia-news%2Fsenior-punjab-cop-an-arjuna-awardee-weightlifter-found-dead-in-canal-4780274%5C%22%3EDalbir%20Singh%20Deol%2C%20also%20an%20Arjuna%20awardee%2C%20was%20found%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20police%20have%20made%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20case%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20key%20accused.%20Police%20have%20arrested%20an%20autorickshaw%20driver%20who%20shot%20Mr%20Deol%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20in%20his%20head%20after%20a%20heated%20argument.%20Mr%20Deol%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20a%20weightlifter%2C%20was%20conferred%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20a%20drug%20addict%2C%20and%20the%20officer%20got%20into%20an%20argument%20when%20the%20latter%20asked%20the%20driver%20to%20drop%20him%20to%20his%20village%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20shot%20Dalbir%20Deol%20from%20his%20service%20pistol%20which%20was%20recovered%20from%20his%20possession%2C%20police%20said.%20His%20body%20bore%20injury%20marks%20and%20was%20found%20lying%20on%20a%20road%20in%20Basti%20Bawa%20Khel%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20where%20he%20was%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20body%20of%20Dalbir%20Singh%20Deol%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20New%20Year's%20Day%20under%20suspicious%20circumstances.%20The%20place%20where%20his%20body%20was%20found%20is%206-7%20kilometers%20from%20Jalandhar.%20We%20have%20arrested%20an%20autorickshaw%20driver%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20in%20the%20case%2C%20%26quot%3BJalandhar%20Police%20Commissioner%2C%20Swapan%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20driver%20refused%20to%20drop%20the%20police%20officer%20to%20his%20village%20which%20led%20to%20a%20scuffle.%20Amid%20the%20argument%2C%20Vijay%20snatched%20the%20service%20pistol%20from%20Mr%20Deol%20and%20fired%20on%20his%20head%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharma%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20accused%20was%20earlier%20charged%20in%20cas