%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sudden%20resurgence%20of%20energy%20was%20felt%20within%20INDIA%2C%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20wonderful%20opportunity%20to%20show%20their%20concern%20about%20the%20marginalised%20social%20groups.%20Kharge%20is%20a%20popular%20mass%20leader%2C%20impressive%20organiser%2C%20committed%20to%20the%20values%20of%20secularism%20and%20social%20justice%20and%20due%20to%20his%20%E2%80%98Dalit%E2%80%99%20social%20location%2C%20one%20can%20assume%20that%20he%20can%20represent%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20socially%20marginalised%20communities%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20pundits%20have%20also%20hinted%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20may%20regain%20its%20lost%20Dalit%20trust%2C%20especially%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20will%20re-emerge%20as%20a%20powerful%20party%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20however%2C%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20will%20not%20necessarily%20provide%20any%20additional%20advantage%20to%20INDIA.%20Instead%2C%20knowing%20the%20political%20history%20of%20caste-based%20social%20antagonisms%2C%20such%20an%20announcement%20may%20polarise%20the%20landed%20and%20agrarian%20castes%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20right-wing%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20and%20Dalit%20leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20with%20Dalit%20leaders%20at%20the%20national%20level%20is%20not%20very%20impressive.%20In%20its%20early%20days%2C%20Congress%20promoted%20leaders%20like%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20to%20challenge%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20Dr.%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20amongst%20the%20Dalit%20community.%20After%20some%20years%2C%20his%20granddaughter%2C%20Meera%20Kumar%2C%20tried%20to%20raise%20alternative%20leadership%20amongst%20the%20Dalits%2C%20challenging%20the%20emergence%20of%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BSP%E2%80%99s)%20Mayawati.%20However%2C%20both%20the%20attempts%20were%20no%20match%20to%20the%20independent%20and%20assertive%20political%20leadership%20that%20Ambedkar%20and%20later%20the%20Dalit%20political%20movement%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0KI3zD_nJ_Q%5C%22%3EWhat%20Happens%20When%20Caste%20Enters%20Mainstream%20Media%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20intellectual%20charisma%20and%20statesmanship%20of%20K.R.%20Narayanan%20that%20provided%20a%20sort%20of%20dignity%20to%20the%20Dalit%20leadership%20within%20the%20Congress%2C%20as%20he%20was%20elevated%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India.%20Otherwise%20the%20Dalit%20leaders%20in%20Congress%20are%20visibly%20dependent%20upon%20the%20organisational%20strength%20of%20the%20party.%20Leaders%20like%20Mukul%20Wasnik%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Shinde%20and%20P.L.%20Punia%20hardly%20gained%20prominence%20in%20national%20politics%2C%20while%20others%20like%20Bhalchnadra%20Mungekar%20remained%20comfortable%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20policy%20consultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%2085vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25190543%2FK-r-narayanan-1-300x250.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25190543%2FK-r-narayanan-1-300x250.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25190543%2FK-r-narayanan-1.jpg%20869w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EK.R.%20Narayanan.%20Photo%3A%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Portrait%20of%20President%20of%20India%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20at%20the%20regional%20level%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20promote%20impressive%20Dalit%20leadership.%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20appointed%20Damodaran%20Sanjivayya%20as%20the%20first%20Dalit%20chief%20minister%20of%20any%20Indian%20state.%20However%2C%20he%20remained%20in%20power%20only%20for%20two%20years%20(1960-62).%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20Jaganath%20Pahadia%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20less%20than%20a%20year%20(June%201980%20to%20July%201981).%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Shinde%20was%20elevated%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20just%20before%20the%202004%20assembly%20elections%2C%20again%20merely%20for%2020%20months.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20party%20selected%20Charanjeet%20Singh%20Channi%20as%20the%20chief%20minster%20just%20before%20a%20year%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%202022.%20During%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20too%20there%20was%20hope%20that%20a%20Dalit%20leader%20may%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20chief%20minster%20after%20Congress%E2%80%99%20victory%20but%20it%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20like%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Dalits%20have%20deserted%20Congress%20and%20adopted%20regional%20leaders.%20However%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20Dalit%20leaders%20at%20crucial%20political%20positions%20have%20helped%20the%20party%20to%20retain%20a%20significant%20Dalit%20vote%20base%20in%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Haryana.%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20further%20encouraged%20Dalit%20voters%20to%20retain%20their%20faith%20in%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20democracy%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20matured%20to%20accept%20people%20from%20socially%20marginalised%20sections%20as%20their%20leaders.%20Especially%20the%20social%20elites%20and%20the%20dominant%20agrarian%20castes%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20appreciate%20Dalit%20leaders%20in%20powerful%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F18125158%2FScreen-Shot-2022-01-18-at-12.51.39-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22863%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F18125158%2FScreen-Shot-2022-01-18-at-12.51.39-PM.png%20863w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F18125158%2FScreen-Shot-2022-01-18-at-12.51.39-PM-300x156.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-576381%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPunjab%20CM%20Charanjit%20Singh%20Channi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40CHARANJITCHANNI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20Congress%20lost%20power%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20as%20the%20dominant%20agrarian%20castes%2C%20especially%20the%20Jats%2C%20had%20deserted%20the%20Congress%2C%20looking%20at%20Channi%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20their%20conventional%20political%20authority.%20It%20was%20the%20remarkable%20political%20inning%20of%20Mayawati%20in%20UP%20that%20showcased%20the%20possibility%20of%20independent%20Dalit-Bahujan%20political%20calibre.%20BSP%20formed%20a%20winnable%20social%20engineering%20formula%20and%20ruled%20the%20state%20effectively.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20times%2C%20BSP%20has%20been%20relegated%20as%20the%20Jatav-dominated%20party%2C%20while%20the%20other%20subaltern%20caste%20groups%20found%20new%20parties%20(including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%20to%20raise%20their%20social%20and%20class%20concerns.%20Even%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20though%20the%20state%20celebrates%20a%20grand%20tradition%20of%20social%20reform%20movements%20and%20anti-caste%20struggles%2C%20Dalit%20political%20leaders%20are%20not%20appreciated%20or%20accepted%20as%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20general%20mass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20fissures%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20social%20engineering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20various%20political%20parties%20have%20projected%20impressive%20Dalit%20leaders%20at%20the%20national%20platform%2C%20many%20of%20them%20are%20belittled%20as%20sectarian%20%E2%80%98Dalit%20leaders%E2%80%99%2C%20unfit%20to%20provide%20good%20leadership%20to%20the%20general%20people.%20The%20traditional%20social%20and%20class%20relationships%20between%20the%20agrarian%20castes%20and%20the%20Dalits%20have%20remained%20hierarchical%2C%20often%20exploitative%20towards%20the%20Dalits%2C%20and%20their%20economic%20and%20political%20empowerment%20is%20not%20appreciated%20by%20the%20dominant%20castes.%20The%20community%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20through%20political%20positions%2C%20class%20mobility%20or%20even%20their%20dignified%20presence%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%2C%20on%20occasion%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20their%20social%20boycott%2C%20violent%20clashes%20and%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20social%20life%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20non-metro%20cities%20and%20in%20the%20rural%20parts%2C%20is%20still%20contaminated%20with%20distrust%2C%20animosity%20and%20jealousy%20between%20various%20caste%20groups.%20Within%20the%20familial%20sphere%2C%20the%20three%20major%20fragments%20of%20the%20society%20%E2%80%93%20social%20elites%2C%20lower%20castes%20and%20Dalits%20%E2%80%93%20still%20operate%20according%20to%20their%20conventional%20caste-based%20cultural%20norms%2C%20often%20showcasing%20distrust%20towards%20each%20other.%20The%20Dalits%20and%20the%20agrarian%20castes%20can%20hardly%20be%20seen%20to%20forge%20close%20social%20associations%2C%20familial%20ties%20or%20engaged%20in%20cordial%20cultural%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmajoritarian-politics-and-the-plight-of-dalits%5C%22%3EMajoritarian%20Politics%20and%20the%20Plight%20of%20Dalits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDifferent%20political%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20hardly%20supported%20any%20substantive%20movement%20to%20build%20social%20harmony%2C%20ensuring%20fraternity%20amongst%20the%20various%20castes%20or%20promoted%20radical%20social%20reforms%20that%20could%20have%20elevated%20the%20social%20stature%20of%20the%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20as%20equal.%20Instead%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20exploited%20such%20social%20fissures%20more%20prudently%20to%20win%20electoral%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConventional%20social%20differences%20between%20caste%20groups%20based%20on%20past%20icons%2C%20social%20rituals%20and%20customs%20are%20consciously%20manipulated%20into%20stiff%20social%20and%20political%20rivalries.%20The%20BJP%20has%20utilised%20various%20caste%20associations%20and%20their%20cultural%20and%20ritualistic%20symbols%20for%20political%20mobilisation.%20In%20UP%2C%20for%20example%2C%20it%20provided%20a%20new%20political%20voice%20to%20different%20caste%20groups%20and%20mobilised%20them%20against%20the%20politically%20assertive%20castes%20(especially%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Jatavs)%2C%20emerging%20as%20party%20of%20the%20subalterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20right-wing%20dispensation%20does%20not%20wish%20to%20disturb%20the%20functional%20social%20normative.%20Instead%2C%20Hindutva%20proponents%20politicise%20caste%20division%2C%20encourage%20patriarchal%20social%20values%20and%20celebrate%20Brahmanical%20cultural%20assets.%20Such%20machiavellian%20tactics%20have%20redefined%20the%20conventional%20grammar%20of%20caste%20politics%20and%20re-emphasised%20the%20subversive%20relevance%20of%20Brahmanical%20caste%20system%20in%20democracy.%20The%20right-wing%20generates%20a%20communal%20social%20psyche%20that%20hardly%20encourage%20the%20arrival%20of%20Dalits%20as%20a%20powerful%20economic%20class%20or%20political%20leaders.%20Therefore%2C%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20promotion%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20will%20overtly%20help%20the%20right-wing%20to%20play%20crude%20caste%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt-300x185.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40kharge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20needs%20EBC%20support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20looks%20comfortable%20with%20the%20support%20that%20it%20gets%20from%20the%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20Muslim%20groups.%20However%2C%20such%20support%20is%20insufficient%20to%20win%20the%20democratic%20battle.%20To%20expand%20its%20social%20support%2C%20the%20Congress%20should%20introduce%20itself%20as%20a%20party%20concerned%20for%20the%20social%20emancipation%20and%20political%20empowerment%20of%20the%20Economically%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20though%20the%20Congress%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20retained%20a%20significant%20vote%20share%20in%20all%20these%20states.%20The%20gap%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20of%208%25%2C%20in%20Chhattisgarh%204%25%20and%20in%20Rajasthan%20it%20is%20a%20mere%202%25.%20The%20CSDS%20election%20survey%20showed%20that%20a%20significant%20majority%20of%20the%20Muslims%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20whereas%20its%20support%20base%20amongst%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20has%20declined.%20To%20win%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20to%20regain%20its%20OBC%20support.%20An%20additional%20shift%20of%20mere%205%25%20among%20OBC%20voters%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%20can%20be%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20overtly%20consolidated%20support%20amongst%20the%20social%20elites%20%E2%80%93%20with%20almost%2070%25%20amongst%20them%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20creating%20a%20solid%20%E2%80%98Upper%20Caste%20Vote%20Bank%E2%80%99.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20with%20the%20socially%20marginalised%20groups%20is%20recent%20and%20these%20groups%20are%20yet%20to%20receive%20substantive%20profits%20for%20their%20association%20with%20the%20right-wing%20party.%20Especially%2C%20for%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20concerns%20of%20the%20EBCs%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20offered%20effective%20policy%20framework%20or%20promoted%20a%20national%20leadership%20amongst%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20can%20engage%20with%20the%20EBC%20issues%20with%20more%20prudence%20and%20sincerity.%20The%20alliance%20should%20promote%20young%20and%20dynamic%20leadership%20amongst%20the%20aspirational%20EBC%20groups%20and%20promise%20them%20substantive%20policy%20packages%20for%20their%20rapid%20economic%20and%20political%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20it%20should%20work%20to%20build%20social%20cordiality%20and%20political%20alliances%20between%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20the%20EBCs%20for%20effective%20political%20and%20social%20change.%20Such%20dynamic%20platform%20of%20unified%20subaltern%20caste%20groups%2C%20may%20allow%20an%20enlightened%20leadership%20amongst%20the%20Dalits%20to%20take%20the%20centre%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fharish-s-wankhede%5C%22%3EHarish%20S.%20Wankhede%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Center%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20School%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704360205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-india-alliance-has-a-caste-conundrum%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22INDIA%20looks%20comfortable%20with%20the%20support%20that%20it%20gets%20from%20the%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20Muslim%20groups.%20However%2C%20such%20support%20is%20insufficient%20to%20win%20the%20democratic%20battle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-india-alliance-has-a-caste-conundrum%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20wants%20me%20arrested%20so%20I%20can't%20campaign%20for%20polls%3A%20Kejriwal%20on%20ED%20summons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704359582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F21%2Ffull%2F1692601402-074.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wants-me-arrested-so-i-can-t-campaign-for-polls-kejriwal-on-ed-summons-124010400348_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Thursday%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20wanted%20to%20arrest%20him%20to%20stop%20him%20from%20campaigning%20for