ut%2C%20ultimately%2C%20he%20didn't%20get%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20you%20work%20for%20Apple%20from%20home%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20work%20is%20possible%20at%20Apple.%20The%20company%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-still-trying-hybrid-rto-work-program-schedule-no-answers-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehybrid%20work%20pilot%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%202022%2C%20which%20requires%20employees%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20including%20Tuesdays%2C%20Thursdays%2C%20and%20a%20day%20determined%20by%20an%20employee's%20manager.%20Apple%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20work-from-home%20weeks%20from%20two%20to%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bretail%20flex%26quot%3B%20program%20for%20retail%20employees%2C%20where%20they're%20assigned%20tasks%20in%20online%20sales%2C%20support%2C%20or%20customer%20service%20when%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20are%20Apple%20salaries%20and%20perks%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESalaries%20at%20Apple%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20job.%20Apple%20says%20its%20base%20pay%20is%20based%20on%20an%20employee's%20skills%2C%20qualifications%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20location.%20Here%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20examples%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20data%20solutions%20software%20engineer%20based%20in%20Cupertino%20has%20a%20salary%20of%20%24138%2C900%20to%20%24208%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20retail%20sales%20financial%20analyst%20based%20in%20Cupertino%20pays%20%24105%2C200%20to%20%24158%2C100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EA%20retail%20manager%20job%20at%20an%20Apple%20store%20in%20Yonkers%2C%20New%20York%20pays%20%2439.59%20to%20%2459.40%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20salary%20is%20part%20of%20a%20total%20compensation%20package%2C%20which%20includes%20employee%20stock%20programs%2C%20family%20medical%20and%20dental%20insurance%2C%20re