%3Cspan%3EAmid%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20and%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20the%20CNF%20unveiled%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D293257796545212%26set%3Da.140698361801157%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estance%20for%20neighbouring%20countries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20July%202023%2C%20notifying%20its%20citizens%20to%20refrain%20from%20engaging%20in%20illicit%20activities%2C%20such%20as%20the%20smuggling%20of%20illegal%20drugs%2C%20and%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20domestic%20politics%2C%20which%20is%20a%20serious%20problem%20for%20India.%20These%20public%20statements%20underscore%20the%20CNF%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20foster%20a%20positive%20relationship%20with%20its%20neighbour%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20new%20governing%20body%20for%20the%20Chin%20by%20the%20CNF.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20formation%20of%20new%20government%20body%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20issue%20that%20may%20cause%20New%20Delhi%20to%20reconsider%20its%20strategy%20is%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20parallel%20government%20in%20Chin%20State.%20From%20December%204-7%2C%202023%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D61554240905507%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChinland%20Council%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20conference%20convened%20with%20235%20delegates%20from%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CNF%2C%20township%20and%20area-based%20administration%20organisations%2C%202020%20elected%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MPs)%2C%20and%20several%20individuals%20from%20different%20Chin%20stakeholders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Chinlung%20City%2C%20a%20newly%20established%20town%20post%20the%20coup%20and%20the%20conference%20ratified%20the%20Chinland%20Constitution%20Many%20observers%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20misled%20when%20the%20conference%20decided%20to%20rename%20%E2%80%98Chin%20State%E2%80%99%20as%20%E2%80%98Chinland%2C%E2%80%99%20raising%20concerns%20over%20whether%20it%20will%20opt%20for%20independence.%20The%20constitution%20explicitly%20calls%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20federal%20union%20which%20enshrines%20full%20self-determination%2C%20equal%20political%20rights%2C%20and%20national%20rights%20for%20the%20Chin.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20seeks%20self-determination%20and%20sovereignty%20over%20its%20area%20rather%20than%20declaring%20itself%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20meeting%20minutes%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20set%20up%20the%20Chinland%20government%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20a%20parliament%2C%20cabinet%2C%20and%20supreme%20court%2C%20within%2060%20days.%20As%20the%20constitution%20stipulates%2C%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20oversee%20the%20effective%20operation%20of%20these%20fundamental%20institutions%20and%20the%20current%20CNF%20chairman%2C%20Pu%20Zing%20Cung%2C%20will%20chair%20the%20Council%20for%20two%20years.%20The%20constitution%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20first%20ever%20Chin%20State%20constitution%20enacted%20by%20the%20Chin%20for%20the%20Chin%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%20meanwhile%20abolishes%20the%20Chinland%20Joint%20Defense%20Committee%20(CJDC)%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20pro-democracy%20armed%20groups%20formed%20after%20the%20coup.%20From%20loosely%20collaboration%20previously%2C%20Chin%20State%20is%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20stronger%20command-and-control%20system%20under%20the%20new%20defense%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolitical%20implications%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20I%20expect%20to%20see%20formulating%20a%20well-coordinated%20and%20comprehensive%20policy%20toward%20alliances%20and%20international%20relations%20under%20the%20new%20government.%20This%20approach%20should%20include%20determining%20how%20to%20collaborate%20or%20adopt%20a%20parallel%20approach%20in%20working%20alongside%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government.%20Now%2C%20having%20approximately%2060%2C000%20of%20internally%20displaced%20peoples%20(IDPs)%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20militarisation%20and%20cyclone%20mocha%2C%20cross-border%20aid%20could%20be%20something%20the%20international%20community%20should%20engage%20with%20the%20Council%20through%20the%20Indian%20Govt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20political%20development%20in%20Chin%20State%20draws%20India%20attention%2C%20to%20address%20its%20interests%20in%20border%20security%2C%20counterbalancing%20China%E2%80%99s%20influence%2C%20and%20effectively%20managing%20its%20major%20business%20ventures%20in%20Myanmar.%20Of%20particular%20concern%20are%20connectivity%20projects%20like%20India%E2%80%99s%20Kaladan%20Multimodal%20Transit%20Transport%20and%20the%20India-Myanmar-Thailand%20trilateral%20highway%20project%2C%20which%20are%20set%20to%20traverse%20Chin%20State.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChin-Mizo%20Relations%20Amid%20Border%20Issues%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recent%20Mizoram%20state%E2%80%99s%20election%20has%20marked%20another%20milestone%20for%20Indo-Myanmar%20relations.%20Though%20we%20do%20not%20expect%20to%20see%20a%20different%20Mizo%20State%E2%80%99s%20refugee%20policy%20under%20the%20new%20Zoram%20People%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20party%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Mizoram%2C%20Lalduhoma%2C%20keen%20to%20maintain%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20Chin.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20publicly%20supports%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Freporter-vlogs%2Fwill-lalduhoma-and-his-young-party-zpm-be-king-or-kingmaker-in-mizoram-polls-736592%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereunification%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Zo%20communities%20(Chin-Kuki-Mizo)%20and%20expresses%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Chin%20people%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20Kuki%20in%20Manipur%20state%2C%20emphasising%20their%20interconnectedness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20robust%20backing%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20the%20Chin%20community%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20fortifying%20their%20ties%20to%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20and%20Mizo%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20Chin%20and%20Mizo%20communities%20have%20shared%20a%20great%20bond%3B%20the%20Mizo%20community%20warmly%20welcome%20and%20generously%20support%20the%20Chin%2C%20offering%20shelter%2C%20food%2C%20and%20unwavering%20assistance%20in%20sharing%20the%20burdens%20faced%20by%20the%20Chin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F11162601%2Frefugee-camp-1024x675.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-628160%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%3A%20A%20Zawlsei%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Aizawl.%20The%20camp%20serves%20as%20home%20to%20Myanmarese%20who%20fled%20the%20military%20persecution%20in%20their%20country.%20Photo%3A%20Sushila%20Sahay%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20tie%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20illicit%20drugs%20have%20been%20a%20major%20concern.%20The%20vice-president%20of%20the%20sub-headquarter%20YMA%20Champhai%2C%20a%20prominent%20youth%20organisation%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzalen.info%2Fvideos%2F7587529004608064%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehighlighted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20recent%20report%20the%20significant%20worry%20among%20the%20Mizo%20community%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eregarding%20the%20influx%20of%20illicit%20drugs%20across%20borders.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Chinland%20government%20also%20has%20to%20make%20an%20impression%20on%20the%20Mizoram%20government%20and%20its%20people%20who%20have%20been%20long%20supporting%20the%20Chin%20people%20as%20well%20as%20New%20Delhi%20with%20regards%20to%20illegal%20drugs%20and%20crimes%20that%20fall%20within%20its%20purview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unodc.org%2Froseap%2Fen%2F2023%2F12%2Fsoutheast-asia-opium-survey-report-launch%2Fstory.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUNODC%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20opium%20cultivation%20in%20Chin%20State%20has%20surged%20by%2010%25%20following%20the%20coup.%20This%20significant%20increase%20poses%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20both%20India%20and%20the%20Chin%20community%2C%20necessitating%20urgent%20attention%20and%20action%20to%20curb%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20sharing%20the%20same%20bloodline%20or%20kinship%2C%20the%20geographic%20separation%20takes%20the%20relationship%20into%20account.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Chin%20has%20to%20establish%20positive%20ties%20with%20the%20Mizoram%20administration%2C%20which%20offers%20individuals%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20the%20region%20access%20to%20healthcare%20and%20education.%20Importantly%2C%20the%20Chin%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20refugee%20issues%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20resettlement%20and%20rehabilitation%20sectors.%20In%20that%20regard%2C%20both%20parties%20must%20be%20concerned%20about%20crossing%20borders%20through%20a%20coordinating%20organisation%2C%20for%20instance%20a%20local%20border%20security%20coordination%20committee%20or%20refugee%20coordination%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20India%20stands%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20in%20its%20relations%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20evolving%20landscape%20of%20the%20Chin%20resistance%20forces%20and%20the%20weakening%20junta.%20The%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20coupled%20with%20political%20changes%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20demands%20a%20cautious%20diplomatic%20strategy%20by%20India%20to%20secure%20its%20interests%20while%20navigating%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20region.%20Given%20that%20Naypyidaw%20has%20lost%20significant%20territorial%20control%2C%20particularly%20since%20the%201027%20operation%2C%20New%20Delhi%20should%20not%20be%20putting%20all%20of%20its%20resources%20behind%20the%20military%20dictatorship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESalai%20Van%20Bawi%20Mang%2C%20a%20Chin%20ethnic%20researcher%20from%20Chin%20State%2C%20explores%20Indo-Myanmar%20relations%20and%20governance%2C%20dedicating%20his%20efforts%20to%20advancing%20democracy%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20federalism%20within%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704357054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04131744%2FScreenshot-2024-01-04-at-1.15.12-e1704354518745.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchin-state-operation-1027-myanmar-mizoram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20establishment%20of%20the%20Chinland%20Council%2C%20coupled%20with%20political%20changes%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20demands%20a%20cautious%20diplomatic%20strategy%20by%20India%20to%20secure%20its