s%20party%20all%20his%20life%20but%20also%20gave%20his%20life%20serving%20the%20Congress%20party.%20And%20today%20it%20would%20give%20him%20great%20joy%20that%20his%20daughter%20is%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps%20and%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04140021%2FEffect-55-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EY.S.%20Sharmila%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Largest%20secular%20party%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20secular%20party%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Sharmila%20said%20that%20her%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20party%20was%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20ongoing%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20still%20the%20largest%20secular%20party%20of%20our%20country.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20always%20upheld%20the%20true%20culture%20of%20India.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20built%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20foundations%20up.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20unwaveringly%20served%20all%20communities%2C%20uniting%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20must%20also%20say%20at%20this%20moment%20that%20as%20a%20Christian%20it%20pained%20that%20such%20cruelty%20took%20place%20in%20Manipur.%202%2C000%20churches%20were%20vandalised%2C%20and%2060%2C000%20people%20became%20homeless.%20And%20that%20kind%20of%20cruelty%20is%20something%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20digest%20till%20this%20day.%20That%20is%20the%20day%20I%20thought%2C%20it%20suddenly%20struck%20me%20that%20this%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20if%20a%20secular%20party%20is%20not%20in%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20am%20joining%20the%20Congress%20and%20merging%20the%20YSR%20Telangana%20Party%20with%20it%20today%20very%20gladly%20because%20I%20know%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20uphold%20all%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20people%20in%20Indian%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%5C%22%3ESharmila%E2%80%99s%20YSR%20Party%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Contest%20Telangana%20Assembly%20Polls%2C%20Offers%20Support%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20revival%20plans%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%E2%80%99s%20induction%20into%20the%20Congress%20comes%20as%20the%20party%20looks%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20in%20the%20state%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20elections%20and%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Manickam%20Tagore%20B%20(who%20had%20earlier%20served%20as%20the%20AICC%20in-charge%20in%20Telangana)%20as%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20party%20in-charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20induction%20comes%20just%20a%20week%20after%20a%20strategy%20meeting%20of%20Andhra%20leaders%20in%20Delhi%20under%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20on%20December%2027%2C%20after%20which%20