ate%20assets%20case%20in%202012-13.%20She%20had%20also%20campaigned%20for%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20absence%20while%20he%20was%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20byelections%20which%20then%20led%20the%20YSRCP%20to%20win%2015%20out%20of%2018%20Assembly%20constituencies%20and%20Nellore%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20that%20went%20to%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20brother%E2%80%99s%20release%20from%20jail%2C%20Sharmila%20again%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20YSRCP%20in%20elections%20to%20the%202019%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20elections%20which%20ended%20the%20TDP%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20differences%20with%20her%20brother%2C%20Sharmila%20took%20out%20another%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fysrtpchief-sharmila-announces-padayatra-from-october-20-101632250454746.html%5C%22%3E%20padyatra%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Telangana.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20she%20had%20political%20ambitions%20but%20in%20Telangana%20and%20not%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20she%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharmilas-ysr-party-wont-contest-telangana-assembly-polls-offers-support-to-congress%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20the%20Congress%20by%20deciding%20to%20not%20contest%20the%20polls.%20Following%20her%20induction%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20is%20happy%20to%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20victory%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20gained%20immense%20confidence%20not%20only%20in%20me%20but%20most%20people%20in%20India%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20And%20that%20yatra%20led%20to%20the%20victory%20in%20Karnataka.%20I%20realised%20that%20will%20have%20a%20domino%20effect%20in%20Telangana%20and%20therefore%2C%20because%20Congress%20stood%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%20in%20Telangana%2C%20I%20graciously%20withheld%20from%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20because%20we%20did%20not%20want%20to%20break%20the%20anti-KCR%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20Congress%20has%20won%20in%20the%20state%20and%20I%20am%20most%20happy%20that%20we%20contributed%20to%20that%20victory.%20It%20was%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%20to%20see%20Mr.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20our%20country%20and%20I%20am%20very%20glad%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20be%20a%20part%20in%20making%20that%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20yet%20announced%20what%20role%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Sharmila%2C%20she%20said%20that%20she%20will%20serve%20the%20party%20in%20%E2%80%9Cwhichever%20responsibility%20with%20loyalty%2C%20dignity%20and%20diligence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20meets%20KCR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20sister%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20called%20on%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Earlier%20on%20Wednesday%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Kakinada%2C%20Jagan%20accused%20opposition%20parties%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdividing%20families%E2%80%9D%20and%20forming%20unholy%20alliances.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20coming%20days%20will%20see%20an%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20in%20party%20alliances%20which%20will%20break%20apart%20families%20and%20even%20bring%20about%20atrocities%2C%20false%20promises%20and%20pave%20way%20for%20deceit%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fopposition-attempting-to-break-families-for-political-gains-ap-cm-jagan-reddy%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fandhra-pradesh%2Fopposition-att