0Numbing%20Effect%20On%20The%20Toolkit%20Nexus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20Hindenburg%20and%20OCCRP%20reports%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20were%20used%20as%20political%20ballistic%20ammunition%20against%20one%20of%20India's%20largest%20business%20conglomerates%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20regulatory%20institutions%20like%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20tool-kit%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20so-called%20investigative%20institutions%20based%20abroad%2C%20NGOs%2C%20aligned%20media%20outlets%20domestic%20and%20overseas%2C%20Left-liberal%20groups%20of%20all%20hues%20and%20sections%20of%20political%20parties%20in%20opposition%2C%20most%20significantly%20the%20Congress%2C%20has%20been%20in%20hyperactive%20mode%20since%20January%2024%20last%20year%2C%20the%20date%20when%20Hindenburg%20published%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20opposition%20forced%20a%20washout%20of%20the%20Budget%20session%20of%20parliament.%20Unrealistic%20demands%20and%20imaginary%20accusations%20and%20claims%20were%20made.%20They%20didn't%20allow%20a%20discussion%20on%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20address%20to%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20parliament.%20That%20too%2C%20when%20it%20was%20President%20Murmu's%20maiden%20address%20to%20parliament%20and%20MPs%20are%20free%20to%20speak%20their%20mind%2C%20for%20or%20against%2C%20in%20these%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20nation%20saw%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20competition%20between%20leaders%2C%20of%20who%20could%20use%20the%20most%20negative%20or%20abusive%20adjectives%20for%20business%20leader%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20his%20group%20and%20his%20perceived%20proximity%20to%20PM%20Modi%20only%20because%20both%20are%20from%20Gujarat.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20convenient%20alibi%20for%20those%20caught%20violating%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20for%20immoral%2C%20unethical%20and%20illegal%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20clearly%20not%20learnt%20lessons%20after%20two%20past%20failures%20-%20the%20Rafale%20and%20Pegasus%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20reposing%20its%20trust%20in%20the%20market%20regulator%20and%20the%20Indian%20regulatory%20mechanism%2C%20has%20not%20just%20smashed%20the%20Hindenburg%20and%20OCCRP%20reports%20and%20their%20patrons%20like%20a%20maverick%20George%20Soros%2C%20but%20has%20also%20had%20a%20numbing%20effect%20on%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20and%20the%20party's%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%20on%20the%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20practically%20indicted%20activist%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20on%20several%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%2C%20however%2C%20brings%20cheer%20not%20just%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20but%20also%20to%20crores%20of%20small%20investors%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20besides%20institutional%20investors%2C%20public%20sector%20banks%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20conclusive%20fact%20that%20emerges%20from%20the%20year-long%2C%20politically%20charged%20dust-raising%20exercise%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20Hindenburg%2C%20which%20originally%20made%20accusations%20through%20a%20voluminous%20report%2C%20booked%20a%20huge%20profit%20by%20short%20selling%20before%20and%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20its%20report%2C%20and%20openly%20admitted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20exposes%20the%20tool-kit%20nexus%20of%20Modi%20government%20haters%20and%20India%20baiters.%20Most%20prominently%2C%20it%20exposes%20the%20likes%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20a%20host%20of%20others.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20has%20left%20them%20without%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20hurt%20the%20Congress%20most%20and%20further%20widen%20the%20conflict%20within%20the%20opposition%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20openly%20rubbished%20Hindenburg%20and%20endorsed%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20former%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20CPM%20leader%20and%20Kerala%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20had%20also%20taken%20a%20soft%20position%20on%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20known%20to%20narrate%20stories%20(his%20own%20version)%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20McDonald's%20and%20Coca%20Cola%20to%20party%20leaders%20and%20workers%2C%20has%20inadvertently%20painted%20himself%20as%20anti-industry%20and%20anti-entrepreneurship.%20That%20image%20is%20certainly%20not%20healthy%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20opposition%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20would%20be%20better%20advised%20to%20read%20the%2046-page%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20before%20venturing%20further%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20keep%20making%20fanciful%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20what%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20in%20the%20order%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20apparent%20regulatory%20failure%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20SEBI%20based%20on%20the%20material%20before%20this%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20must%20refrain%20from%20substituting%20its%20own%20wisdom%20over%20the%20regulatory%20policies%20of%20SEBI.%20The%20scope%20of%20judicial%20review%20when%20examining%20a%20policy%20framed%20by%20a%20specialized%20regulator%20is%20to%20scrutinise%20whether%20it%20violates%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20any%20provision%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20any%20statutory%20provision%20or%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facts%20of%20this%20case%20do%20not%20warrant%20a%20transfer%20of%20investigation%20from%20SEBI.%20In%20an%20appropriate%20case%2C%20this%20Court%20does%20have%20the%20power%20to%20transfer%20an%20investigation%20being%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20authorized%20agency%20to%20an%20SIT%20or%20CBI.%20Such%20a%20power%20is%20exercised%20in%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20when%20the%20competent%20authority%20portrays%20a%20glaring%2C%20wilful%20and%20deliberate%20inaction%20in%20carrying%20out%20the%20investigation.%20The%20threshold%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20investigation%20has%20not%20been%20demonstrated%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reliance%20placed%20by%20the%20petitioner%20on%20the%20OCCPR%20report%20to%20suggest%20that%20SEBI%20was%20lackadaisical%20in%20conducting%20the%20investigation%20is%20rejected.%20A%20report%20by%20a%20third-party%20organization%20without%20any%20attempt%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20its%20allegations%20cannot%20be%20regarded%20as%20conclusive%20proof.%20Further%2C%20the%20petitioner's%20reliance%20on%20the%20letter%20by%20the%20DRI%20is%20misconceived%20as%20the%20issue%20has%20already%20been%20settled%20by%20concurrent%20findings%20of%20DRI's%20Additional%20Director%20General%2C%20the%20CESTAT%20and%20this%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sanjay%20Singh%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704356220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnu5or0go_adani-power-reuters_625x300_02_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-numbing-effect-on-the-toolkit-nexus-4798204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20Hindenburg%20and%20OCCRP%20reports%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20were%20used%20as%20political%20ballistic%20ammunition%20against%20one%20of%20India's%20largest%20business%20conglomerates%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20regulatory%20institutions%20lik