sday%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20summons%26quot%3B%20were%20being%20sent%20to%20him%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam%20case.%20Crying%20foul%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%2C%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20like%20ED%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20get%20him%20arrested.%20Kejriwal%20on%20Thursday%20held%20a%20press%20briefing%20shortly%20after%20he%20skipped%20the%20third%20summon%20issued%20to%20him%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20liquorgate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdelhi-liquorgate-bjp-wants-to-arrest-me-using-ed-cbi-says-arvind-kejriwal-after-skipping-third-summon%2Farticleshow%2F106536909.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Row%20Over%20PM%20Selfie%20Points%2C%20Indian%20Railways%20Tighten%20RTI%20Norms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFollowing%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20selfie%20points%20with%20Prime%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image%20installed%20at%20railway%20stations%2C%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20tightened%20norms%20for%20Zonal%20Railways%20furnishing%20information%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%20As%20per%20the%20changed%20rules%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20must%20go%20through%20general%20managers%20of%20zonal%20railways%20or%20divisional%20railway%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Board%2C%20in%20an%20advisory%20sent%20out%20to%20general%20managers%2C%20on%20December%2028%2C%202023%2C%20said%20it%20had%20come%20to%20its%20notice%20that%20lately%20%E2%80%9Cquality%20of%20replies%20to%20RTI%20applications%20handled%20by%20Zonal%20Railways%20and%20other%20field%20units%20had%20deteriorated%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fstriking-fear-on-hit-and-run-accident-cases-and-section-106-of-the-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita%2Farticle67703190.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTimelines%20for%20disposal%20of%20RTI%20applications%20were%20surpassed%20in%20many%20cases%20resulting%20in%20a%20large%20number%20of%20appeals%20filed%20before%20the%20First%20Appellate%20Authority%20or%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%2C%20not%20only%20increasing%20the%20quantum%20of%20work%20but%20bringing%20disrepute%20to%20the%20organisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tide%20over%20these%20problems%2C%20the%20advisory%20said%20a%20decision%20had%20been%20made%20that%20timelines%20for%20disposal%20prescribed%20in%20the%20Act%20should%20be%20complied%20with%20at%20any%20cost.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20also%20said%20to%20ensure%20quality%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20going%20forward%20must%20be%20approved%20respectively%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20general%20manager%20(GM)%20in%20Zonal%20Railways%20and%20divisional%20railway%20managers%20(DRMs)%20in%20the%20Divisions.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20replies%20to%20first%20appeals%20received%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act%20need%20to%20be%20shown%20to%20the%20GM%20and%20DRM%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20advisory%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Railways%20had%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20and%20Chief%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20to%20furnish%20information%20sought%20by%20petitioners.%20Neither%20general%20managers%20nor%20divisional%20railway%20managers%20had%20any%20role%20to%20play%20as%20appellate%20or%20competent%20authority%20as%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20quoting%20sources%20in%20the%20Southern%20Railway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20have%20been%20brought%20into%20force%20after%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20each%20permanent%20selfie%20booth%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20image%20costs%20Rs%206.25%20lakh%20while%20each%20temporary%20selfie%20booth%20costs%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%2C%20which%20is%20the%20approved%20cost%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communication%20under%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting.%20The%20above%20information%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20furnished%20by%20the%20Central%20Railway%20in%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20further%20deepened%20after%20the%20authorities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcentral-railways-pro-transferred-without-notice-after-releasing-costs-of-modi-selfie-points%5C%22%3Etransferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20Central%20Railway%E2%80%99s%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20Shivaji%20Manaspure%20against%20the%20backdrop%20that%20it%20was%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20deputy%2C%20Abhay%20Mishra%2C%20as%20Deputy%20General%20Manager%20of%20Central%20Railway%2C%20disclosed%20the%20information%20pertaining%20to%20selfie%20points.%20Manaspure%20had%20been%20in%20the%20post%20for%20seven%20months%20while%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20said%20post%20is%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20sought%20to%20underline%20that%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20done%20as%20an%20act%20of%20punishment%20due%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20caused%20to%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EShahenshah%20ki%20raza%2C%20sach%20ka%20inaam%20saza%3C%2Fi%3E%20(King%20rewards%20truth%20with%20punishment)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gandhi%20had%20written%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20at%20Indian%20Railways%20refute%20the%20allegations%20that%20Manaspure%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20due%20to%20the%20information%20revealed%20on%20selfie%20points.%20They%20say%20it%20was%20only%20due%20to%20operational%20reasons.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20say%20revised%20guidelines%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20RTI%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20a%20former%20railway%20employee%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20information%20on%20selfie%20points%20through%20an%20RTI%20application%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CRTIs%20filed%20to%20seek%20response%20on%20expenditure%20incurred%20%5Bon%20the%203D%20booths%5D%20from%20Southern%2C%20Western%20and%20Northern%20Railways%20did%20not%20elicit%20any%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-row-over-pm-selfie-points-railways-tightens-rti-norms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20changed%20rules%2C%20all%20RTI%20replies%20from%20Indian%20Railways%20must%20go%20through%20general%20managers%20of%20zonal%20railways%20or%20divisional%20railway%20managers.%20So%20far%2C%20public%20information%20officers%20and%20chief%20public%20information%20officers%20handled%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-row-over-pm-selfie-points-railways-tightens-rti-norms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lt%20Governor%20Asks%20CBI%20To%20Investigate%20Delhi%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20%26quot%3BFake%20Tests%20Scam%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20corruption%20allegations%20in%20diagnostic%20tests%20done%20at%20Delhi's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20allegedly%20ran%20fake%20radiology%20and%20pathology%20tests%20without%20any%20patients%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20had%20also%20flagged%20the%20matter%20on%20September%2020%2C%20following%20which%20seven%20doctors%20posted%20at%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20were%20removed.%20Some%20doctors%20would%20come%20to%20the%20clinics%20very%20late%20and%20still%20mark%20full%20attendance%2C%20while%20others%20would%20bunk%20the%20whole%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20remove%20the%20health%20secretary%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20ago%2C%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20had%20ordered%20another%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20into%20alleged%20supply%20of%20substandard%20medicines%20to%20Delhi%20government%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20case%2C%20initial%20investigation%20found%20that%20doctors%20who%20had%20not%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20clinics%20had%20been%20marked%20as%20present.%20The%20clinics%20continued%20to%20prescribe%20diagnostic%20tests%20for%20patients%20who%20did%20not%20exist%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20infrastructure%20was%20conceptualised%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20provide%20primary%20healthcare%20accessible%20to%20communities%20in%20Delhi%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20hyperlocal%20clinics%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20not%20only%20the%20population%20of%20Delhi%20but%20also%20migratory%20and%20floating%20population%20from%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20which%20makes%20for%20a%20considerable%20patient%20load.%20There%20are%20also%20many%20areas%2C%20particularly%20slums%2C%20where%20the%20poor%20do%20not%20get%20easily%20get%20primary%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-03%2Faam-aadmi-mohalla-clinic-650_650x400_51489764972.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20corruption%20allegations%20in%20diagnostic%20tests%20done%20at%20Delhi's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Takes%20Revenge%20On%20Cheating%20Boyfriend%2C%20Reports%20Him%20For%20Unpaid%20Taxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20for%20sharing%20here%20innovative%20revenge%20plot%20against%20cheating%20boyfriend.%20Ava%20Louise%2C%20an%20OnlyFans%20model%2C%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20TikTok%20in%20which%20she%20claimed%20she%20reported%20the%20man%20to%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20of%20the%20United%20States%20government%20for%20unpaid%20taxes.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EDistractify%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20video%20she%20posted%20has%20gone%20massively%20viral%2C%20amassing%20over%203.8%20million%20views.%20It%20appears%20that%20Ms%20Louise%20fulfilled%20the%20conditions%20mentioned%20on%20the%20IRS%20website%20to%20receive%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.distractify.com%2Fp%2Fwoman-reports-ex-to-irs-for-reward-money%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDistractify%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20OnlyFans%20model%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20ex%20confided%20in%20me%20he%20never%20paid%20his%20taxes%2C%20then%20cheated%20on%20me%20a%20few%20months%20later%20I%20reported%20him%20to%20the%20IRS%20and%20collected%20over%20100k%20in%20reward%20money.%20I'm%20spending%20his%20money%20daily%20while%20he's%20facing%20years%20in%20jail.%20The%20female%20rage%20is%20a%20powerful%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20claim%20shared%20by%20Ms%20Louise%2C%20she%20pocketed%20around%20Rs%2083%20lakh%20by%20reporting%20her%20ex-boyfriend%20for%20unpaid%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20IRS%20whistleblower%20programme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20Ms%20Louise's%20account%2C%20she%20appears%20to%20have%20made%20use%20of%20the%20whistleblower%20programme%20of%20the%20agency%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20taxes%20and%20enforcing%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcompliance%2Fwhistleblower-office%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20IRS%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Whistleblower%20Office%20pays%20monetary%20awards%20to%20eligible%20individuals%20whose%20information%20is%20used%20by%20the%20agency.%20%26quot%3BThe%20award%20percentage%20depends%20on%20several%20factors%2C%20but%20generally%20falls%20between%2015%20and%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20proceeds%20collected%20and%20attributable%20to%20the%20whistleblower's%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20further%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20eligible%2C%20a%20person%20has%20to%20submit%20a%20claim%20of%20non-compliance%20exceeding%20over%20%242%2C000%2C000%20by%20an%20individual.%20Further%2C%20the%20accused%20should%20have%20a%20gross%20annual%20income%20of%20over%20%24200%2C000%20%26quot%3Bfor%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20tax%20years%20in%20question%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20such%20an%20incident%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20three%20women%20in%20China%20teamed%20up%20to%20expose%20a%20man%20who%20posed%20as%20a%20love%20interest%20and%20cheated%20them%20of%20100%2C000%20yuan%20(Rs%2011%2C67%2C982).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%2C%20the%20Shanghai%20man%20has%20received%20two%20years%20and%20six%20months%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20before%20that%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20US%20tracked%20her%20cheating%20boyfriend%20using%20Apple's%20AirTag%20and%20ran%20over%20him%20with%20a%20car%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bar.%20She%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9j49e3v_ava-louise_625x300_04_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20TikTok%20video%20where%20Ava%20Louise%20shared%20her%20story%20has%20amassed%20more%20than%203.8%20million%20views.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Dismisses%20Petition%20Of%20Indian%20Arrested%20In%20US%20Murder%20Plot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20petition%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20United%20States%20of%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20pertains%20to%20international%20law%20and%20it%20must%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20courts%20in%20other%20countries.%20The%20court%20also%20said%20it%20cannot%20interfere%20because%20the%20matter%20is%20a%20sensitive%20one%20and%20has%20international%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20is%20in%20prison%20in%20Prague%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20and%20the%20United%20States%20has%20sought%20his%20extradition%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20for%20hire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20one%20of%20Mr%20Gupta's%20family%20members%20seeking%20instructions%20being%20given%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20appropriate%20diplomatic%20help%20-%20including%20consular%20access%20and%20legal%20aid%20-%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20outset%20itself%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20say%20we%20don't%20think%20we%20can%20do%20anything%20in%20this%20regard%20or%20give%20any%20relief.%20The%20only%20intervention%20we%20can%20look%20into%20is%20consular%20access%20as%20per%20Vienna%20Convention%2C%20which%20you%20yourself%20say%20in%20the%20petition%20that%20you%20have%20got.%20The%20matter%20pertains%20to%20international%20law%2C%20we%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20courts%20in%20foreign%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20CA%20Sundaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B(Give)%20at%20least%20some%20direction%20to%20the%20ministries.%20He%20(Nikhil%20Gupta)%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20in%20the%20country%20at%20all.%20He%20has%20not%20got%20consular%20access.%20Petition%20has%20been%20wrongly%20interpreted.%20I%20have%20been%20given%20the%20extradition%20order%20yesterday...%20Legal%20assistance%20is%20all%20I%20am%20asking.%20An%20interpreter%20and%20translator%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20for%20the%20government%20to%20decide.%20If%20the%20petitioner%20wants%20to%20approach%20the%20government%2C%20the%20Centre%20may%20take%20it%20as%20a%20representation%20from%20the%20petitioner.%20It%20is%20a%20sensitive%20matter%20for%20the%20government%20also%20as%20it%20has%20international%20ramifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sundaram%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Gupta%20has%20been%20kept%20in%20solitary%20confinement%20and%20that%20he%20needs%20the%20ministry's%20help%20to%20defend%20himself.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20relief%20and%20dismissed%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20hearing%20on%20December%2015%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20Mr%20Gupta's%20family%20to%20approach%20a%20court%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%20Even%20in%20that%20hearing%2C%20it%20had%20made%20the%20point%20that%20this%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20sensitive%20matter%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Petition%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20was%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20on%20a%20business%20trip%20when%20he%20was%20illegally%20detained%20at%20Prague%20Airport%20on%20June%2030.%20It%20states%20that%20there%20were%20irregularities%20in%20his%20arrest%20and%20no%20formal%20arrest%20warrant%20was%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claims%20that%20consular%20access%20to%20Mr%20Gupta%20has%20not%20been%20granted%20and%20he%20has%20also%20not%20been%20given%20the%20right%20to%20contact%20his%20family%20in%20India%20or%20seek%20legal%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20torture%20have%20also%20been%20made%2C%20and%20the%20petition%20states%20that%20Mr%20Gupta%20faces%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life%20because%20he%20is%20locked%20in%20a%20prison%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Got%20Access%20Thrice'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20last%20month%20that%20India%20had%20got%20consular%20access%20to%20Mr%20Gupta%20on%20at%20least%20three%20occasions%20and%20is%20extending%20the%20necessary%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20has%20charged%20Mr%20Gupta%20with%20conspiring%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%20The%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20holds%20citizenship%20of%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20is%20accused%20of%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%2C%20who%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20undercover%20US%20federal%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fc9cdh8ao_us-prison-generic-us-jail-generic-getty_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramifications-supreme-court-dismisses-petition-of-indian-arrested-in-us-murder-plot-4797725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dismissing%20the%20petition%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20US%20of%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20it%20must%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20courts%20in%20other%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramifications-supreme-court-dismisses-petition-of-indian-arrested-in-us-murder-plot-4797725%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramifications-supreme-court-dismisses-petition-of-indian-arrested-in-us-murder-plot-4797725%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramif