20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20chart%20based%20on%20government%20data%20from%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcleanmobilityshift.com%2Fev-dashboard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVahan%20Dashboard%20aggregated%20by%20Clean%20Mobility%20Shift%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shows%2C%20only%2072%2C930%20four-wheeled%20electric%20vehicles%20were%20newly%20registered%20in%20India%20in%202023.%20While%20this%20is%20almost%20double%20the%20number%20of%202022%2C%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%E2%80%99s%20shift%20to%20e-mobility%20is%20mainly%20focused%20on%20two-wheelers%20like%20mopeds%20as%20well%20as%20e-rickshaws%20and%20other%20three-wheelers%2C%20which%20comprised%2056%20and%2038%20percent%2C%20respectively%2C%20of%20the%20total%20EV%20sales%20in%20the%20country%20this%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectric%20vehicles%20had%20a%20market%20share%20of%206.3%20percent%20in%202023%2C%20a%20considerable%20increase%20compared%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20of%20just%20below%20one%20percent.%20According%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F12%2F29%2Findia-ev-market-2024%2F%3Fguccounter%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%20by%20TechCrunch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20the%202023%20growth%20bolstered%20by%20more%20than%20%24600%20million%20in%20government%20subsidies%20via%20the%20FAME-II%20program%20can%20be%20carried%20over%20into%202023.%20The%20current%20government-set%20target%20is%20a%2030%20percent%20EV%20market%20share%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20global%20perspective%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F5623%2Felectric-vehicle-market-in-china%2F%23topicOverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20still%20the%20standard%20bearer%20of%20the%20ongoing%20push%20for%20fleet%20electrification.%20CleanTechnica%20data%20shows%20that%2022%20percent%20of%20all%20new%20cars%20sold%20in%20the%20East%20Asian%20country%20in%202022%20were%20fully%20electric.%20When%20figuring%20in%20plug-in%20hybrids%2C%20the%20EV%20market%20share%20stood%20at%2030%20percent%20in%20the%20corresponding%20year.%20In%20Europe%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20had%20a%20market%20share%20of%2023%20percent%20of%20all%20newly%20registered%20vehicles%2C%20while%20battery%20electric%20vehicles%20alone%20made%20up%2014%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Infographic%3A%20How%20Many%20EVs%20Are%20Sold%20in%20India%3F%20%7C%20Statista%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F31486%2Felectric-vehicle-sales-in-india-by-year-and-type%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Infographic%3A%20How%20Many%20EVs%20Are%20Sold%20in%20India%3F%20%7C%20Statista%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.statcdn.com%2FInfographic%2Fimages%2Fnormal%2F31486.jpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EYou%20will%20find%20more%20infographics%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchartoftheday%2F%5C%22%3EStatista%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20this%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fchart%2F31486%2Felectric-vehicle-sales-in-india-by-year-and-type%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704342611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04094214%2FElectric_auto_rickshaw_in_Siliguri.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fchart-how-many-evs-are-sold-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20shift%20to%20e-mobility%20is%20mainly%20focused%20on%20two-wheelers%20like%20mopeds%20as%20well%20as%20e-rickshaws%20and%20other%20three-wheelers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenv