.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F05155821%2Fnaravane.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%2C%20has%20made%20a%20series%20of%20revelations%20in%20his%20upcoming%20memoirs%2C%20including%20being%20handed%20a%20%E2%80%9Chot%20potato%E2%80%9D%20in%20dealing%20with%20Chinese%20troop%20movement%20in%20August%202020%2C%20and%20how%20the%20Agnipath%20tour%20of%20duty%20scheme%20caught%20the%20armed%20forces%20by%20surprise%20and%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbolt%20out%20of%20the%20blue%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Naravane%20retired%20as%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20on%20April%2030%2C%202022%20and%20has%20since%20completed%20his%20PhD%20in%20defence%20and%20strategic%20studies%20from%20Punjabi%20University%2C%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20219px)%2085vw%2C%20219px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03191905%2Fimage-1683-219x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22219%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03191905%2Fimage-1683-219x300.png%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F03191905%2Fimage-1683.png%20456w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691502%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%3A%20An%20Autobiography%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20General%20Manoj%20Mukund%20Naravane.%20(Penguin%2C%20April%2030%2C%202024)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%20titled%20%3Cem%3EFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20reviewed%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20last%20month.%20It%20also%20put%20out%20five%20news%20stories%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fauthor%2Fmanash-pratim-bhuyan%2F%5C%22%3Ebased%20on%20the%20excerpts%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20book.%20The%20book%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20released%20this%20month%20and%20has%20been%20open%20for%20pre-orders%20since%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20revelations%20from%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%20based%20on%20the%20published%20excerpts%20in%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHanded%20a%20hot%20potato%20on%20Ladakh%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20excerpt%20of%20the%20book%20published%20in%20PTI%2C%20General%20Naravane%20writes%20about%20the%20night%20of%20August%2031%2C%202020%2C%20following%20a%20tense%20situation%20arising%20out%20of%20Chinese%20PLA%20moving%20tanks%20and%20troops%20in%20Rechin%20La%20mountain%20pass%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20writes%20how%20the%20armed%20forces%20were%20left%20to%20their%20own%20devices%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20massive%20security%20challenge%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20as%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20appropriate).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20writes%20that%20a%20hundred%20different%20thoughts%20%E2%80%9Cflashed%20through%E2%80%9D%20his%20mind%20after%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20conveyed%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20RM%20(Raksha%20Mantri)%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20which%20he%20did%2C%20by%20about%202230%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CXi%20Jinping%20won%E2%80%99t%20forget%20June%2016%2C%202020%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20also%20writes%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-army-officers-killed-china-galwan-valley%5C%22%3EGalwan%20Valley%20clash%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2016%2C%202020%20when%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20the%20saddest%20days%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20he%20also%20writes%20that%20the%20Chinese%20president%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20not%20forget%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJune%2016%20is%20(Chinese%20President)%20Xi%20Jinping%E2%80%99s%20birthday.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20day%20he%20will%20forget%20any%20time%20soon.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20Chinese%20and%20the%20PLA%20had%20suffered%20fatal%20casualties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wrote%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Csavagery%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Chinese%20response%20showed%20that%20they%20had%20suffered%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20men%20who%20were%20in%20Chinese%20hands%20had%20been%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20they%20had%20seen%20several%20bodies%20being%20fished%20out%20of%20the%20river.%20Whenever%20that%20happened%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20beatings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sheer%20savagery%20of%20their%20response%20was%20in%20itself%20indicative%20of%20the%20losses%20they%20had%20suffered.%20Initially%2C%20they%20did%20not%20admit%20to%20any%20casualties%20at%20all%3B%20then%20many%20months%20later%2C%20admitted%20to%20four%20or%20five%20killed%2C%20including%20the%20CO%20on%20their%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20mention%20in%20the%20excerpts%20released%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fchina-releases-10-indian-army-soldiers-majors-talks-ladakh-1690509-2020-06-19%5C%22%3Eof%20the%2010%20Indian%20soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20four%20officers%2C%20who%20were%20held%20captive%20for%20three%20days%20before%20being%20released%20by%20the%20Chinese%20army%2C%20as%20per%20some%20reports%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7ak7tshMJEU%3Fstart%3D21%26feature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%26quot%3B%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%26quot%3B%20%7C%20Agniveer%20%7C%20Indian%20Army%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgnipath%20scheme%20%E2%80%98bolt%20out%20of%20the%20blue%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20had%20first%20sounded%20out%20the%20PM%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20more%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20short-service%20option%20at%20the%20soldier%20level%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20scheme%20for%20officers%20that%20was%20already%20in%20vogue%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20as%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20SSC%20officers%20are%20taken%20each%20year%2C%20likewise%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20jawans%20would%20be%20similarly%20enrolled%20and%20released%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98tour%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20option%20of%20re-enlisting%20for%20another%20tour%2C%20if%20found%20to%20be%20fit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20nothing%20much%20happened%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20was%20considering%20this%20proposal%2C%20but%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20applicability.%20In%20the%20PMO%20formulation%2C%20not%20only%20should%20the%20complete%20intake%20of%20the%20year%20be%20short-service%20based%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20become%20a%20tri-service%20matter%2C%20it%20now%20fell%20on%20the%20CDS%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20to%20take%20the%20proposal%20forward%2C%20albeit%20with%20the%20Army%20remaining%20the%20lead%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20were%20taken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fagnipath-scheme-job-destruction-creation-modi-government%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Is%20a%20Marketing%20Trick%20in%20Which%20Job%20Destruction%20Is%20Being%20Sold%20as%20Job%20Creation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20questioned%20wisdom%20of%20government%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20also%20writes%20that%20he%20never%20%E2%80%9Cquestioned%E2%80%9D%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20government%20on%20not%20being%20appointed%20the%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20I%20am%20asked%20as%20to%20why%20I%20was%20not%20appointed%20as%20the%20CDS.%20My%20response%20has%20always%20been%20that%20I%20never%20questioned%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20government%20when%20they%20made%20me%20Chief%2C%20so%20why%20should%20I%20do%20so%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20what%20rank%20you%20retired%20at%2C%20but%20the%20reputation%20you%20retired%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAgniveer%20scheme%20bulldozed%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20excerpts%20were%20released%20by%20PTI%2C%20reports%20said%20that%20the%20book%20was%20yet%20to%20receive%20requisite%20clearances%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVaidhi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcolkt%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40colkt%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20and%20Chitra%20Ji%3A%20Do%20you%20feel%20that%20the%20new%20book%20%E2%80%9CFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%E2%80%9D%20may%20undergo%20a%20major%20revision%3F%20The%20new%20book%20by%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Mukund%20Naravane%20Ji%20needs%20Modi%20Govt%20approval%20before%20release%20in%20the%20market..%20%E2%98%98%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%8D%81%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpBCzFXGcyW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FpBCzFXGcyW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dharma%20(%40Dharma4X)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDharma4X%2Fstatus%2F1741332139398807845%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20release%20of%20the%20excerpts%20on%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20memoirs%20%E2%80%9Cconfirmed%20what%20had%20been%20commonly%20believed%20when%20the%20Agnipath%2FAgniveer%20