%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20their%20success%2C%20about%2040%20farmers%20have%20joined%20Sanjay%20and%20his%20cooperative%20%E2%80%98Bless%20All%20Pearl%20Farmer%20Producer%20Company%E2%80%99.%20Together%2C%20they%20have%20planted%2050%2C000%20oysters%20and%20collaborated%20with%20companies%20like%20GKP%20Pearl%20Farm%20of%20Solapur%20and%20Namo%20Pearl%20Farm%20in%20Chandrapur%20to%20sell%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cooperative%20is%20set%20to%20harvest%20its%20second%20batch%20in%20the%20upcoming%20December%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESix%20tips%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20group%20was%20able%20to%20generate%20a%20handsome%20profit%20in%20their%20very%20first%20attempt%2C%20the%20success%20rate%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20was%20not%20as%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20progressive%20farmer%20travelled%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20%E2%80%94%201%2C400%20km%20from%20his%20village%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20formal%20training%20in%20oyster%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F232818%2Fpearl-cultivation-earns-lakhs-urban-garden-cultured-freshwater-pearls-online-classes-business-how-to-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20attended%20a%20seven-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20how%20to%20source%20raw%20material%2C%20how%20to%20nucleate%20oysters%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20pearl%20designs%20that%20are%20in%20demand%2C%20what%20food%20to%20offer%20oysters%2C